longBusinessSummary: Torrent Gold Inc., a resource exploration company, acquires, explores for, and evaluates mineral properties in Canada and the United States. It explores for silver, gold, copper, zinc, and base metal properties. The company was formerly known as Raindrop Ventures Inc. and changed its name to Torrent Gold Inc. in April 2022. Torrent Gold Inc. was incorporated in 2018 and is headquartered in Vancouver, Canada.
